videos.headline: California fools Arizona for game's first TD
videos.description: Ross Bowers fakes the pass and hands it off to Patrick Laird for an 8-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Taylor breaks free for long TD run
videos.description: J.J. Taylor finds a hole for a 30-yard touchdown run to tie the game at 7 in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Tate dazzles with 76-yard TD run
videos.description: QB Khalil Tate, who became Arizona's starter just two weeks ago, runs for his FBS-best third touchdown of at least 70 yards.

videos.headline: Arizona forces game's first takeaway
videos.description: Lorenzo Burns intercepts Ross Bowers' pass and returns it for 21 yards to the 50-yard line.

videos.headline: Arizona's offensive line creates a hole for Green
videos.description: Zach Green runs up the middle for a 13-yard touchdown run to give Arizona a two-touchdown lead.

videos.headline: Arizona picks off Bowers for second time
videos.description: Jarrius Wallace intercepts Ross Bowers' pass   in the end zone for a touchback.

videos.headline: McMorris catches first TD pass of the season
videos.description: Ross Bowers finds Malik McMorris in the corner of the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown to bring the Golden Bears within 7.

videos.headline: Brown beats defender downfield for 56-yard TD
videos.description: Khalil Tate connects with Shun Brown for a 56-yard touchdown catch and run.

videos.headline: Bowers takes it himself for California TD
videos.description: Ross Bowers runs it in for a 4-yard touchdown to bring the Golden Bears within 7.

videos.headline: Laird just gets into the end zone for game-tying TD
videos.description: Patrick Laird reaches over the goal line for an 18-yard touchdown run to tie the game at 28.

videos.headline: California picks off Tate late in the fourth quarter
videos.description: With the score tied at 28 late in the fourth quarter,  Ashtyn Davis intercepts Khalil Tate's pass and returns 31 yards.

videos.headline: Kanawai Noa gives Cal the lead in first OT
videos.description: Ross Bowers connects with Kanawai Noa for a 13-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Green sends it into second OT
videos.description: Zach Green runs it up the middle for a 25-yard touchdown to send the game into a second overtime.

videos.headline: Tate throws a dime to Wolma for TD
videos.description: Tate escapes defenders and finds Bryce Wolma for a 22-yard touchdown in second overtime.

videos.headline: Enwere bullies his way into the end zone
videos.description: Vic Enwere fights his way into the end zone on a second attempt for a 1-yard touchdown run.
